feedback:
Good attempt at Pataka! You're on the right track. Here's what to focus on:

**What to adjust:**
• The most important adjustment is to gently bend your thumb and press it against the side of your palm.
• Try to keep your fingers closer together, so they are parallel and touching.

**You're doing well:**
• You are keeping your fingers straight, which is a great start for Pataka!

Keep practicing - you're making progress!
